TEXT 2360 1592 Left 2 !.param VIN=9.6\n.tran 8m startup\n; === OUTPUT VOLTAGE (Abstract: 12.20V) ===\n.meas TRAN Vout_before AVG V(OUT) FROM 4m TO 5m\n.meas TRAN Vout_after AVG V(OUT) FROM 6m TO 7m\n; === LOAD TRANSIENT (Abstract: 127mV droop, 1.5A step) ===\n.meas TRAN Vout_droop MIN V(OUT) FROM 5.1m TO 5.4m\n.meas TRAN Vout_droop_mV PARAM (Vout_before-Vout_droop)*1000\n.meas TRAN Vout_droop_pct PARAM (Vout_before-Vout_droop)/Vout_before*100\n.meas TRAN Vout_recovery FIND TIME WHEN V(OUT)=12.15 CROSS=2 TD=5m\n; === OUTPUT RIPPLE (Abstract: 184mV) ===\n.meas TRAN Vout_ripple PP V(OUT) FROM 6m TO 7m\n.meas TRAN Vout_ripple_mV PARAM Vout_ripple*1000\n; === INDUCTOR CURRENT ===\n.meas TRAN IL_peak MAX I(L1) FROM 4m TO 5m\n; === EFFICIENCY (Abstract: 94.83%) ===\n.meas TRAN Pin AVG V(IN)*(-I(V1)) FROM 6m TO 7m\n.meas TRAN Pout AVG V(OUT)*I(I1) FROM 6m TO 7m\n.meas TRAN Eff PARAM Pout/Pin*100\n.meas TRAN Iin_avg AVG I(L1) FROM 6m TO 7m\n.meas TRAN P_D1 AVG (V(SW)-V(OUT))*I(D1) FROM 6m TO 7m\n.meas TRAN P_M1 AVG V(SW)*Id(M1)         FROM 6m TO 7m\n.meas TRAN P_L1 AVG I(L1)*I(L1)*0.014    FROM 6m TO 7m\n.meas TRAN P_loss_total PARAM Pin-Pout\n.meas TRAN P_M2 AVG V(n007, in)*Id(M2) FROM 6m TO 7m
TEXT 952 1672 Left 2 ;=== VALIDATED MODEL with series FDS4435A Protection (17-Apr-2026, D2 removed from power path) ===
TEXT 952 1696 Left 2 ;M1: IRF7811 N-MOSFET (validated, SI4894BDY for hardware)
TEXT 952 1728 Left 2 ;M2: FDS4435A P-MOSFET (simulation proxy for DMP3099L)
TEXT 952 1752 Left 2 ;R6/R7: 549k/100k RUN pin UVLO divider (VIN,enable = 8.1V)
TEXT 952 1776 Left 2 ;C1a: 77uF (7x22uF derated), C1b: 12uF (2x10uF derated), C5: 100uF electrolytic
TEXT 952 1800 Left 2 ;D1: MBR735, L1: 10uH, M2 series protection (D2 zener removed - was in power path causing 6.5W loss)
